<h2 id="_filtering_tags">3. Filtering tags</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>There are three possibilities for filtering tags. You can filter them by <strong>section</strong>, <strong>language</strong> or <strong>name</strong>.</p>
</div>
<div class="imageblock">
<div class="content">
<img src="{{plugin_path('PlentyManual')}}/images/basics/working-with-plentymarkets/assets/ENG-Einstell-Grundeinstell-Tags03-SI.png" alt="ENG Einstell Grundeinstell Tags03 SI">
</div>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><em>Image 3: filtering tags</em></p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The following table explains the <strong>filters</strong> for tags:</p>
</div>
<table class="tableblock frame-all grid-all spread">
<colgroup>
<col style="width: 50%;">
<col style="width: 50%;">
</colgroup>
<thead>
<tr>
<th class="tableblock halign-left valign-top">Setting</th>
<th class="tableblock halign-left valign-top">Explanation</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Section</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Select a section (table 1) or the setting <strong>All</strong>. Once you have clicked on the field, a drop-down menu will open that displays the various sections.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Language</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Select a language or the setting <strong>All</strong>. Once you have clicked on the field, a drop-down menu will open that displays the various languages.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Name</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>Enter a name. A list of results will be displayed once you have entered the first letter. If all languages were selected, then all languages will be included here as well. However, only the value that was entered under <strong>Name</strong> will be displayed.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
